  "description": "Variation of condition 2 (approved plans) of planning permission 2019/3464 dated 23/12/2019 for &#x27;erection of a roof extension to provide office space (Use Class B1a) including rooftop plant enclosure for air-conditioning units; change of use of the ground floor and basement from offices (B1a) to a café (Use Class A3); and alterations to the ground floor façade.&nbsp;The amendment seeks to replace rainwater pipes, amend the windows at ground and first floor levels, replace the security shutter at ground floor level, change the design of balustrade at third floor level and amend parapets at roof level.&nbsp;",
  "title_number": [],
